Stone Free
================
 
Stone Free is a greasemonkey script to help you discover free alternatives to consumer goods. It currently works with Amazon and Craigslist.

http://userscripts.org/scripts/show/39557



Usage
========

1 - Add the script via greasemonkey
2 - Edit the script to use the Craigslist site nearest to you
3 - Visit an Amazon product page and marvel at the free alternatives found on Craigslist

 
 
